data.description: Welcome to Lakes of Mount Dora! This beautiful and spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bath home is located in a 55+ community, with no rear neighbors for added privacy. As you enter through the glass-paned front door you will be drawn to the high ceilings and windows that provide ample natural light. The home features tile throughout, upgraded stainless steel appliances, and upgraded window treatments which make this home both functional and lovely. The living area is ideal for entertaining guests or relaxing alone with its sliding glass doors opening onto a screened-in patio overlooking the garden. The dining room has large windows and bar seating creating an open plan with the living room. For added convenience this home also has a tankless water heater system installed so you never have to worry about running out of hot water! Residents at Lakes of Mount Dora can enjoy access to three pools, playground, cable & internet included as well as irrigation services from St John's River. There are also plenty of planned community trips and events available too! Don’t miss out on this amazing opportunity – call us today to schedule your viewing appointment!
